and find that bullet.

68
00:03:53,149 --> 00:03:55,818
No, no, no. Don't.
No, you're not gonna put that in her.

69
00:03:55,902 --> 00:03:58,529
-[woman 2] Oh, I'm in. Feel that?
-[woman 1 exclaims]

70
00:03:58,613 --> 00:04:00,281
