87
00:04:49,038 --> 00:04:54,210
And anything beyond a simple "yes"
is gonna just super suck for your face.

88
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:58,006
Look, your client is a half-wit,
fuckstain war criminal.

89
00:04:58,089 --> 00:04:59,132
