92
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,764
Just get him on the phone.

93
00:05:07,265 --> 00:05:08,808
Let's just fucking get nuts.

94
00:05:08,891 --> 00:05:09,851
What do you say?

95
00:05:09,934 --> 00:05:11,728
