104
00:05:31,414 --> 00:05:32,665
I don't care.

105
00:05:34,584 --> 00:05:35,585
Go, go!

106
00:05:38,546 --> 00:05:39,672
[tires screech]

107
00:05:42,633 --> 00:05:44,594
