115
00:06:16,292 --> 00:06:18,127
You hit one more person, and I'm walking.

116
00:06:18,211 --> 00:06:20,505
-You hear that?
-A lot of backseat-driving going on.

117
00:06:21,798 --> 00:06:22,965
