I'm starting to feel it.

154
00:08:54,659 --> 00:08:56,953
I'm feeling fucking carsick.

155
00:08:59,413 --> 00:09:01,415
<i>♪ This is not another story ♪</i>

156
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:04,752
<i>♪ This is not another drill ♪</i>

157
