-[beep]

235
00:12:42,511 --> 00:12:44,138
-Go, guy. Go, go, go, go!
-[engine roars]

236
00:12:48,142 --> 00:12:49,852
[police radio chatter in Italian]

237
00:12:52,396 --> 00:12:53,773
You gotta lose that police chopper.

238
00:12:54,273 --> 00:12:55,107
